---
// FaqContent
---
      <main class="main-wrapper">
        <section class="section_hero-faq">
          <div class="padding-global">
            <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-large w-container">
              <div class="master_faqs">
                <div
                  data-w-id="1816d543-6134-ae41-b3d1-e9c0856792d3"
                  style="opacity:1"
                  class="headline_faq-hero"
                >
                  <div
                    data-wf--tag--variant="depth"
                    class="master_label w-variant-9a59c277-b838-5a8e-f25e-39f9204dca4d"
                  >
                    <div class="label-large">FAQ</div>
                  </div>
                  <h1>ОТВЕТЫ НА ВАШИ ВОПРОСЫ</h1>
                  <div class="subtext_faq">
                    <p class="text-size-large">
                      Ответы на частые вопросы о ценах, услугах и записи.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div
                  data-w-id="4685c8c1-6341-8eb8-bad2-0fa172f41a3d"
                  style="opacity:1"
                  class="wrap_faq-block"
                >
                  <div class="headline_faq-block">
                    <h2 class="heading-style-h4 margin-0">General</h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq-block">
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Что входит в стандартную уборку?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Стандартная уборка включает кухню, санузел, жилые комнаты, полы, удаление пыли и вынос мусора. Этого достаточно, чтобы поддерживать дом в чистоте.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Сколько стоит уборка?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Цена зависит от площади и частоты уборки. Для еженедельных, раз в две недели и ежемесячных планов действуют автоматические скидки.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Сколько длится уборка?<br />
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Обычно уборка занимает 2–3 часа в зависимости от площади и состояния. Генеральная уборка — дольше.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Проверяете ли вы клинеров?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Да. Каждый клинер проходит проверку, собеседование и отбор по нашим стандартам качества.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Используете ли вы эко-средства?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Да — все наши средства нетоксичны и безопасны для детей и животных.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Нужно ли давать чаевые?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Tipping is optional but appreciated. You can tip in
                          cash or via card after your cleaning.<br />
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Можно ли заказывать одного и того же клинера?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Да — при регулярных уборках мы по возможности закрепляем за вами одного клинера.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div
                  data-w-id="9df1917b-48ef-a490-1500-ef57bcb92339"
                  style="opacity:1"
                  class="wrap_faq-block"
                >
                  <div class="headline_faq-block">
                    <h2 class="heading-style-h4 margin-0">
                      Cleaning &amp; Equipment
                    </h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq-block">
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Нужно ли предоставлять свой инвентарь?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Нет. Клинер приезжает со всем инвентарём и эко-средствами.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                           Can I request specific products (e.g., unscented)?<br />
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Yes — just tell us in the booking notes and we’ll
                          adjust.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Моете ли вы внутри духовки, холодильника и шкафов?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Это входит в генеральную уборку. Можно добавить при оформлении заказа.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Моете ли вы окна?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Да — мойка окон изнутри доступна как дополнительная услуга.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Справитесь ли вы с шерстью животных?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Конечно. Наш инвентарь и пылесосы рассчитаны именно на это.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Do you move furniture?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          We move lightweight items but not heavy furniture for
                          safety reasons.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Do you wash dishes or handle laundry?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Light dishwashing is included. Laundry is not included
                          unless added as a special service.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Do you clean after renovation or construction?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Yes — our post-reno option covers dust removal,
                          surfaces, and floors after contractors leave.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div
                  data-w-id="6d5698b0-94e8-50f5-48af-a1e9d5ab3823"
                  style="opacity:1"
                  class="wrap_faq-block"
                >
                  <div class="headline_faq-block">
                    <h2 class="heading-style-h4 margin-0">
                      Booking &amp; Policies
                    </h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="faq-block">
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Can I book a one-time cleaning?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Yes — one-time, recurring, and deep cleanings are all
                          available.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          How far in advance should I book?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          We recommend booking 2–3 days ahead. Same-day slots
                          are occasionally available.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          What if I need to cancel or reschedule?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          You can reschedule or cancel up to 24 hours before
                          your appointment at no charge.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          What happens if the cleaner is late?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          If a cleaner is running behind, we’ll notify you
                          immediately and adjust your time if needed.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          What if I’m not satisfied with the cleaning?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Contact us within 24 hours and we’ll send someone back
                          for free — no questions asked.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Do I need to be home during the cleaning?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          No — as long as we can access the apartment. Many
                          clients leave keys with the doorman.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          How do I pay?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          You pay securely online when booking. No cash needed.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expandable-single">
                      <div class="expandable-top">
                        <div class="text-size-large text_body-bold">
                          Do you offer recurring discounts?
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq_animated-box">
                          <div class="faq-horizontal"></div>
                          <div class="faq-vertical"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="expandable-bottom">
                        <p class="faq-paragraph">
                          Yes — weekly, bi-weekly, and monthly plans include
                          automatic savings on each cleaning.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
      <section class="section_features">
        <div class="padding-global">
          <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-large w-container">
